  </knowledge>

  <steps>
    <step order="1">Read the PB-009 section of `notes/handoffs/120-pb-audit.md` end-to-end. Note the current description, configJson, node graph, and any Power Automate consumers.</step>
    <step order="2">Draft the embedding-friendly description per FR-43: one sentence purpose + trigger words + output format + document type hints + NO project-task refs. Aim for 1-2 sentences, 200-400 chars.</step>
    <step order="3">Draft the JPS `$ref` composition referencing `skill:NDA Review` (SKL-003) + `knowledge:NDA Standards` (KNW-006) + `knowledge:Defined Terms` (KNW-005). Use the JPS-v1 schema shown in design.md §WP6 sketch.</step>
    <step order="4">Draft the `sprk_jpsmatchingmetadata` JSON: `documentTypes` (e.g., `["nda", "non-disclosure-agreement", "confidentiality-agreement"]`), `intents` (e.g., `["summarize"]`), `triggerPhrases` (e.g., `["summarize this NDA", "review NDA", "NDA summary"]`).</step>
    <step order="5">Identify the target `sprk_playbookcode` (`summarize-nda`) and confirm uniqueness against the audit's other-playbook codes.</step>
    <step order="6">Specify node-graph adjustments needed for Path 3 (single-node, action with embedded JPS `$ref` in systemPrompt; configJson destination=workspace + widgetType=structured-output-stream).</step>
    <step order="7">Write the plan at `notes/handoffs/121-pb009-remediation-plan.md` with sections: (1) Description Rewrite, (2) JPS $ref Composition, (3) sprk_jpsmatchingmetadata Payload, (4) sprk_playbookcode Target, (5) Node-Graph Adjustments, (6) Task 130 Application Checklist.</step>
    <step order="8">Update TASK-INDEX.md: task 121 → ✅.</step>
  </steps>

  <tools>
    <tool name="Read">120-pb-audit.md, design.md, skills.json, knowledge.json</tool>
